<style>
    /* Custom styles here */
    body {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        color: #333;
    }

    .jumbotron {
        background-image: url('/img/HtunMyatAung/about_bg.png');
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-position: center;
        height: 400px;
        width:100%;
        color: #000;
        text-align: left;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 0px;
    }

    

        .jumbotron h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
        }

    .content-section {
        padding: 50px 0;
    }

    .team-member {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

        .team-member img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 5px solid #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .team-member h3 {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .team-member p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
        }
</style>
<div class="container-fluid py-4">

    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-4">About Swift Foods</h1>
            <p class="lead">We provide the best food for you.</p>
            <p class="lead">Feel the taste of most popular foods from anywhere and anytime.</p>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="container content-section">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    "Our vision is to become the leading online food ordering pla
                    tform, known for our commitment to customer satisfaction and 
                    culinary diversity. We aspire to empower local restaurants by 
                    expanding their reach and providing customers with a user-friendly 
                    platform that caters to all their dining preferences. We envision a 
                    future where ordering food online is synonymous with a delightful and 
                    hassle-free experience, driven by innovation and a passion for great food."
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <p>Our mission is to provide a seamless and convenient
                    online food ordering experience, connecting customers
                    with their favorite local restaurants. We strive to offer
                    a diverse range of culinary options, ensuring quality and
                    satisfaction for every meal delivered. By leveraging technology,
                    we aim to simplify the process of discovering and ordering
                    delicious food, making mealtime easier and more enjoyable for
                    everyone.
                </p>

                </div>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="~/img/HtunMyatAung/hma_profile.jpg" alt="Team Member 1">
